e><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>跳水-杨连杰让中国横扫梦想继续走上正轨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-yang-lian-win-mens-synchronised-10m-platform-2024-07-29/</link><description>周一，杨浩和连俊杰在男子双人10米跳台比赛中表现出色，为中国队包揽全部八块跳水金牌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:10:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-yang-lian-win-mens-synchronised-10m-platform-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国名将盛在巴黎夺得第二枚射击金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-south-korean-ban-wins-womens-10-metre-air-rifle-gold-2024-07-29/</link><description>周一，中国选手盛立浩在沙托鲁射击中心表现出色，夺得男子10米气步枪比赛的第二枚巴黎奥运会金牌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 08:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-south-korean-ban-wins-womens-10-metre-air-rifle-gold-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>香港维权人士擅自带出监狱投诉表格被定罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-activist-convicted-taking-complaint-form-out-prison-without-2024-07-29/</link><description>香港一家法院周一判定民主活动人士周文豪和他的律师胡菲丽丝去年未经授权将一份供监察员使用的投诉表格带出监狱。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 08:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-activist-convicted-taking-complaint-form-out-prison-without-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责美日在海上问题和军事扩张问题上的“不实指控”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rebukes-us-japan-false-accusations-maritime-issues-military-expansion-2024-07-29/</link><description>中国外交部周一表示，美国和日本之间的联合声明在海上问题上“错误地指责”中国，并指责中国正常的军事发展和国防政策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:47:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rebukes-us-japan-false-accusations-maritime-issues-military-expansion-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国7月份制造业活动继续下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-manufacturing-activity-seen-extending-decline-july-2024-07-29/</link><description>路透周一的一项民意调查显示，中国7月份工厂活动可能连续第三个月萎缩，由于旷日持久的房地产危机和就业不稳定拖累经济增长，官员们需要推出进一步刺激措施的预期依然存在。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-manufacturing-activity-seen-extending-decline-july-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，台湾第二季度经济增长放缓，但受到人工智能热潮的支撑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-q2-economic-growth-seen-slowing-supported-by-ai-boom-2024-07-29/</link><description>路透社周一的一项民意调查显示，尽管人工智能技术的高需求推动了出口强劲，但依赖贸易的台湾第二季度经济增长可能放缓。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 05:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-q2-economic-growth-seen-slowing-supported-by-ai-boom-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：亚洲因鸽派利率希望而反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-29/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 04:40:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>四国外长谴责危险的南海行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/quad-foreign-ministers-meet-tokyo-talks-maritime-security-cyber-2024-07-29/</link><description>澳大利亚、印度、日本和美国外长周一表示，他们对南中国海的恐吓和危险行为感到严重关切，并承诺加强该地区的海上安全。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 02:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/quad-foreign-ministers-meet-tokyo-talks-maritime-security-cyber-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>法院称碧桂园清算听证会推迟至明年一月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-january-next-year-court-says-2024-07-29/</link><description>香港一家法院周一将寻求碧桂园清算请愿书的听证会推迟至 2025 年 1 月 20 日，这让这家陷入困境的中国开发商有了喘息的机会，该开发商正试图敲定离岸债务重组计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 02:16:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-january-next-year-court-says-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>债权人寻求破产程序后，中国恒大的电动汽车部门下线</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/shares-china-evergrande-new-energy-vehicle-set-open-up-9-2024-07-29/</link><description>周一早盘，中国恒大新能源汽车股价下跌 7%，此前该公司旗下两家子公司的个人债权人寻求法院批准这些子公司进入破产程序并进行重组。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 01:41:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/shares-china-evergrande-new-energy-vehicle-set-open-up-9-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>美元在央行会议繁忙的一周开始时保持稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-eases-nikkei-jumps-central-bank-meetings-loom-2024-07-29/</link><description>美元周一小幅上涨，交易员们准备迎接繁忙的一周新闻，其中包括周三美联储和日本央行的政策决定，以及周五的美国 7 月就业报告。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 01:31:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-eases-nikkei-jumps-central-bank-meetings-loom-2024-07-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>